# Income Insurance Non Reinsurance Recoveries Amount

## identifier
de8482

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, for the duration of the relevant period, of revenue from recoveries other than those from reinsurance in respect of insurance claims. This item is determined in accordance with the Accounting Standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Income.Insurance.NonReinsuranceRecoveries.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.05
- period=duration
